    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v0
    v2 = (v2 - (wp.cos(tmp + 0.24) - wp.abs(tmp + 0.10)))
    v1 = (0.56 - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.09) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.51)))
    data[tid] = v0
